      "role": "user",
      "content": "[Roleplay Context: The setting is a fading digital archive. My character, Elara, is a sentient program realizing that the server hosting her world is being decommissioned. The lights are dimming, and the code is fracturing.]\n\nElara: (staring at the flickering horizon of failing data clusters) It’s all just... noise now. If the server goes dark, if I'm just wiped... does any of this even matter? Was there ever a point to any of it?",
